snippet.title: Cursed Bet - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2460900/Cursed_Bet/

Cursed Bet is a horror game where you play from a body camera perspective. Enter the abandoned preschool, the subject of terrible rumors, in the midnight. Struggle the cursed doll Ebeleen as you investigate the school's dark past. Will you be able to destroy him and his curse?
